{"tid":46243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「一號九龍山頂」竟在荃灣 發展商: 新界屬於九龍","createTime":"2016-12-19T13:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T03:47:29.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ccaee059c4a7aef51ec710ed51d947c829f6bbd","tid":46243,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:47:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/program/12257775/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fprogram%2F12257775%2F&d=AB%2BcY2C%2FDevFsiJ4lyasjWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=01344fb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fprogram%2F12257775%2F&h=f3628dc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/program/12257775/</a> <br />\n<br />\n《一手住宅物業銷售條例》生效三年來，銷監局共收到一百八十宗涉及失實陳述、發佈誤導性資料等投訴。 <br />\n<br />\n這個樓盤有著威猛的名字，名為「一號九龍山頂」。在哪裡？樓盤其實是在荃灣油柑頭寶豐台八號，門牌並非一號，地點不在九龍，位置亦不是山頂。 <br />\n<br />\n銷監局指出，發展商有責任確保樓盤名稱及宣傳不會對公衆或準買家造成混淆，如發現任何涉嫌違反《一手物業銷售條例》的情況，會作出跟進調查。 <br />\n<br />\n「一號九龍山頂」不在九龍，「何文田山畔」？都不會在何文田。樓盤位於高山道，銷監局曾特意提醒買家，根據規劃署分區計劃大綱圗，該處屬於紅磡區。 <br />\n<br />\n新界屬於九龍一部份? 咁上水既樓咪可以改為「九龍北一號」?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6224a7d27acae07013c110a7ee176f3b2edb0233","tid":46243,"uid":5382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:54:07.000Z","msg":"好撚on9<br />\n現代指鹿為馬<br />\n含撚啦"},{"pid":"422df7e847a6de6b42b309216563dc6f52111687","tid":46243,"uid":5705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:56:18.000Z","msg":"地產商大曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2abf157f6cbda9d3187d9c154c51be347e95db4","tid":46243,"uid":57329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T13:56:58.000Z","msg":"古有神聖羅馬帝國 今有一號九龍山頂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n既不神聖 亦非羅馬 更不是帝國"},{"pid":"1f2abf85